5:
This place is wild... Is this what adults
do for entertainment?
8: Everything is very colorful and flashy.
13:
Should we really have brought those
two here?
16:
Quit your worrying, old man. Nothing
THAT bad goes down in here.
21:
Yeah! It's not like you have to get
ID'd to walk in!
40:
Entering a casino is one thing, but
underage drinking?!
46:
Take whichever one catches your
fancy!
55:
Ta-da! A special garnish, courtesy
of my illusion magic!
63:
How marvelous... Could I also have
one?
71:
That was magical. All the people
nearby were super interested too.
79: Would you like to give it a go, miss?
83: Yes, sirree! Let me at it!
87: I'll show you what I'm made of...
108: It was only an illusion, after all.
127:
Illumine... What'd you do to the
machine?
131:
Teehee, I dunno what you're talking
about!
137:
Explaining to the employee what
happened was pretty awkward...
141:
Sorry... I thought it'd be a fun
surprise, so I couldn't help myself.
145:
The entertainer in you never rests,
does she? I understand you're
passionate, but we came here to
take a break.
155:
All right, Illumine. No more
entertaining othersfocus on
entertaining yourself!
158:
Thanks for waiting, folks. It's about
time for our Show of Spectacles to
start! Gather around the stage on
the first floor!
161: Did I just hear "Show of Spectacles"?
164:
...And that concludes our
contortionist's show! Thanks for
watching!
167:
I have never seen a man's body
twist like that before.
171:
The fire-breather was amazing too! I
thought for sure the flames were
going to singe us!
175:
How did you find it, Illumine? Isn't it
nice to sit back and be the audience
sometimes?
188: Nope, I can't hold back any longer!
197:
Illumine, illusionist of light, is about
to take the stage!
200:
What's this? Have we got ourselves
a surprise performance?!
207:
"Whoa, which one's the real one?"
"Who is she?!"
"She's amazing! I'm so glad I
stopped by!"
210: So much for taking a break, huh?
218: Thank you, thank you! I love you all!
